{"tid":1641554,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家不妨試下喺黨鐵站勸下人唔好到搭","createTime":"2019-10-09T11:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T11:38:29.000Z","uid":141577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"33b4516b75ed7338035045e3e928ee088f09f131","tid":1641554,"uid":141577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:14:25.000Z","msg":"今朝返工時間行去巴士站<br />\n途中經過黨鐵站見到仍然係咁多人搭<br />\n突然好衝動咁嗌 有良知嘅唔好再搭黨鐵啦唔該 黨鐵出賣我地呀仲搭 俾啲骨氣得唔得<br />\n我唔知實際有無人真係因為聽到之後會唔搭<br />\n但係我嗰下feel 到有啲人係有猶豫<br />\n<br />\n大家不如做多一步啦 <br />\n有時間嘅 企喺站度好言相勸下啲人<br />\n我諗其實好多人都不恥黨鐵嘅所作所為<br />\n只係差俾人提醒一下"},{"pid":"972e74f631efb2a9a48912f8fe5a2e0bcdb25892","tid":1641554,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e2e0b45486ec0a2292885afb3542ad4535be02","tid":1641554,"uid":141577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"972e74f631efb2a9a48912f8fe5a2e0bcdb25892","tid":1641554,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:38:29.000Z","msg":"唔排除真係有人差你推多一下<br />\n無成本 怕咩做多少少"}]}